{"tid":1611874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港女車神李慧詩昨為港市民出聲 今早專頁被消失","createTime":"2019-10-02T05:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T05:29:23.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ed9f47f8c60776e2becc822e700f5e80da9d020e","tid":1611874,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:29:23.000Z","msg":"李慧詩Facebook專頁消失<br />\n<br />\n昨天於個人Facebook專頁發文、寫上「今天出門小心避雨　沒有雨傘要早點回家」的香港單車代表李慧詩，其專頁突然於今天消失；本網記者曾嘗試以名字作搜尋，已無法找到其專頁。<br />\n<br />\n#李慧詩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/641243772668505/posts/2259166770876189?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F641243772668505%2Fposts%2F2259166770876189%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdDDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=527302f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/641243772668505/posts/2259166770876189?sfns=mo</a>"}]}